                  </div><!-- /.accordion-image -->

                  <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>
                      Teletherapy is the live delivery of our best-in-class speech-language & feeding services in the convenience of your home or school by live video online (via an internet connection) <a href="/about">with our team of Speech-Language Pathologists</a>.  Your child meets 1-on-1 with their SLP via video conference. No additional technical set-up, knowledge or software is required by the parent.
                    </p>

                  </div><!-- /.accordion-content -->

